Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:03.05,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Flowing water has no form.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.05,0:00:04.96,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A blowing wind can't be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:06.63,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All cases can be freely deduced!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:08.38,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A visitor from France!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.38,0:00:10.73,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Murderous intent harmonizes with the melody of the piano!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.73,0:00:12.39,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.39,0:00:14.01,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.01,0:00:16.39,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:54.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Kana Amusement Group\Nis a very big company.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:54.75,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Yoshinori Kana (35)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.44,0:01:58.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What would the chairman of such a company want to talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.75,0:02:04.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we're going to be making a CD\Nfor Gerard Tenma at our company.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:08.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we're going to be holding a private party upon the signing of the contract...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:12.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How nice! Tenma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is finally going to make his debut in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:13.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:14.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.79,0:02:19.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a mysterious Japanese singer who is the talk of the French world of {\i1}chanson{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:22.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one knows anything about his personal history, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:25.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed that you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:28.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since the day we decided on the date of the party,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:32.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,eerie things have been happening around his wife Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:34.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eerie things?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:36.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Repeated phone calls,\Nwith no one on the other end...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.77,0:02:39.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bouquet of roses from an unknown sender...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.10,0:02:40.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.25,0:02:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:46.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blackmail...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.55,0:02:49.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Those who do not realize my love will surely fall to the pits of hell..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:53.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We got the other one yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:56.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The curtains will be opened to commence the party of revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enjoy a party of terror to your heart's content..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The party will be held in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:06.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't cancel it now,\Nbut I'm worried about my wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea who this may be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We are carrying out the contract process in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the only ones who know that there is going to be a party
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:18.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,are my wife and I, and the other four who are scheduled to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.79,0:03:25.72,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Three Days Later
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.23,0:03:25.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"You left me behind all alone,\Nbut I still have not forgotten you."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.11,0:03:27.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"My eyes are always on you."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:32.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I hear your voice and I am just so delighted."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.03,0:03:33.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What on earth is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:34.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:38.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the Japanese lyrics to Tenma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s\N"The Red Nocturne of Love"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:45.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hm... "I'll send you a flower a day..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:51.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"A red rose, a marigold, a lobelia,\Na bright red dahlia, and a love song..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:55.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"You are forever mine."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:04:00.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I wonder what she likes about a song like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy that I'm going to get to see Tenma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:07.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is work now, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:12.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're supposed to be members of the Morita family, a friend of the chairman, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:13.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't have them finding out that I'm a top-notch detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:19.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. You don't look like one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.75,0:04:24.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh. You two better behave yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:25.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I{\i0} should be the one saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:37.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Going from the gate to the entrance of the house by car
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:39.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is like what I've seen in foreign movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:49.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is really some house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.53,0:04:52.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They must be millionaires!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.91,0:05:07.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, doesn't it look like a castle that you see in horror movies?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:15.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no, thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:19.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it was such a fine day until just a while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:22.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you want to see Gerard?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Being scared is another thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:30.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are Morita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:33.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm Morita.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.03,0:05:41.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:47.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Morita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! We've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:54.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for inviting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:05:59.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome. Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.31,0:06:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's my secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:08.59,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Masayo Tokudaiji (24)\NSecretary
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:06.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Masayo Tokudaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:11.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:21.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the reception room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:25.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The artwork here is also fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:32.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all my wife's taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:35.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come this way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:40.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, may I take a look around your residence before doing so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:42.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokudaiji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:45.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please show them around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:47.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:47.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:51.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll show them around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:55.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's my wife, Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:59.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's the president of the company group,\NKana Music Publishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:04.68,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Misaki Kana (32)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:04.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:10.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please prepare things in the kitchen, Masayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:26.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your wife doesn't like me, does she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:35.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the room right above the large reception hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:37.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beyond it is the piano room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.18,0:07:44.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, how wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:47.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You even have a spiral corridor in the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.42,0:07:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:55.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, runt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:57.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't lay a finger on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:08:00.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not all that fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:03.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although it's just a decoration,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:06.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's made of the same materials\Nand in the same way as the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:09.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In other words, it is the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:12.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The room next to the piano room is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come this way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:19.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This room also looks very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:22.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this a picture of your wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:25.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:29.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was taken ten years ago today, in Fiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:31.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We belonged to the same music club in our university days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We went steady for a year, and then got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:42.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, how I envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:55.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:57.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:08:59.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.11,0:08:59.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person hung up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.18,0:09:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:07.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They hung up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does this kind of thing happen often?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:12.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:15.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In a hoarse, male voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:17.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,things like "mon amie" and "je t'aime" are whispered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:20.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when I answer, the phone is hung up immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:23.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have no idea who it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:25.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:28.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Together with a letter, I got this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:33.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was this taken without you being aware?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:38.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is what I found together with the bunch of marigolds I found at the front door this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:40.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This seems to have been taken yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.55,0:09:45.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm scared because I feel like someone's always watching me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:47.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}After the rose is the marigold...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Always watching...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:52.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Worry no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.39,0:09:56.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I, Kogoro Mouri, will protect you,\NMisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, with my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chairman, the guests have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:05.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:11.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to have kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brother, this is Gerard Tenma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:20.59,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Michel Anglade (40)\NManager
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:20.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Michel. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:24.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my older brother\NYoshinori Kana, and his wife Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:26.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:29.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is Tenma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:35.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. He had some other work to attend to,\Nso he'll be here about 30 minutes late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brother, who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's an old friend of mine, Morita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:42.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those are his children, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:45.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Morita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, this is my younger brother Hideki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:49.83,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hideki Kana (30)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:48.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is the vice-president of Kana Music Publishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:53.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brother, may I have a word with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:54.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:57.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come this way and have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, what delicious-looking dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:03.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't forget why we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you invite outsiders here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:12.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is an important time when we have to sign a contract with Gerard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:14.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.18,0:11:19.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You leave for France on your own and suddenly bring Gerard along...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:23.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thinking of the company, I don't see anything wrong in what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:25.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the company?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.46,0:11:28.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess so, because if this doesn't work out,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:30.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you can't make yourself look good to Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:33.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:35.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hear you've been persistently hitting on Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:37.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who told you such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:40.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about you and Tokudaiji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:42.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rumor's going around all over the company!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:45.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous! There is nothing going on between her and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm going to make this contract go through, no matter what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:06.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's about time for Gerard to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:08.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go wait for him by the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:09.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:12.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But first, I need to use the men's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:18.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please get the next dish ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:19.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:23.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have anything to drink, Morita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:24.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go get you some.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:27.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:31.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you excuse me while I go fix my make-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:39.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't drink too much, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:41.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:42.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you have to go guard Misaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, Dad! You've got work to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:51.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't possibly go into a room where a lady is fixing her make-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:53.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:54.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:56.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The power went out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:12:59.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lightning hit somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:01.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:07.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:16.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:21.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The door's locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.81,0:13:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:28.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:34.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:35.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Misaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:38.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dammit. Where'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Misaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:49.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:52.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody switched off the breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.32,0:13:56.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:58.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Somebody suddenly attacked me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:02.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:05.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lobelia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:08.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just as I thought, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.65,0:14:14.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, flowers by that name come up in that song too, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:15.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That song?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:17.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean "The Red Nocturne of Love"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:19.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rose, marigold, lobelia...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:23.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that all the flowers that the person had sent up to now are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"My eyes are always on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:30.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hear your voice and I am just so delighted."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:33.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that someone is threatening Misaki
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,according to the lyrics of Gerard Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Threatening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:42.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It means that someone is stalking your beautiful wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.83,0:14:46.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although I know we are all in the midst of a party,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:48.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to question all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:51.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you the one who turned off the breaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.17,0:14:56.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. On my way here, the breaker at the top of the stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:14:58.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where were you at that time, Hideki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Morita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:07.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'm not actually Morita, but Kogoro Mouri, a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogoro... Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.98,0:15:10.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That famous...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:12.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.67,0:15:15.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Misaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you locked the door, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:18.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as I was about to fix my make-up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:22.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the lights went out and I was attacked from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't see the attacker's face?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:29.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't see very clearly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he was wearing a cape, and had a facial expression...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looked like a foreigner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:38.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like a foreigner?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me? Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:43.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, but where were you at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:47.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to the front door to meet Gerard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lights went out and I came inside because it started to rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:54.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw Hideki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, and heard a voice scream, "Help!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:57.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We came here together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:15:59.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you cut it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Michel{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is an important guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:06.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gerard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:12.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looks like the attacker...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:15.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:18.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is our main guest tonight, Gerard Tenma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:21.99,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Gerard Tenma (34)\NChanson singer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There seemed to be no one downstairs, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:24.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We had a little incident here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:27.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I speak to you downstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:29.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come with me too, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:36.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The door of the room was locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:39.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Which means the attacker was already in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.51,0:16:43.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Everyone who left the large reception hall beforehand had the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:47.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So, who switched the breaker off?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:49.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could there be more than one attacker?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:50.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.12,0:16:52.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What is this a piece of?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:55.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The crack is still new...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:57.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's more small debris nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.94,0:17:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, the size is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:06.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this a trace of?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where were you all when the incident occurred?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:14.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:16.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I panicked when the lights went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in the kitchen checking on the cake the mistress had baked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:25.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tenma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you were drenched, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:28.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because I got out of the taxi by the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:30.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:35.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, why don't we take a break then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That kid again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:51.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear, can you go get medicine from my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:58.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:03.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The picture that was taken last night was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:05.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.05,0:18:11.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They seem to have struggled pretty hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:18.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Misaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Gerard Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:21.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is dated ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:24.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,two weeks before Misaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} got married!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.80,0:18:29.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, Dad's going to scold you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.51,0:18:31.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:33.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, er, well, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Show it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:37.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:51.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you have a relationship with Misaki in the past?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:52.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:54.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brother, what a rude thing to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:55.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hideki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:57.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you knew about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:18:59.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Why would I do such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.55,0:19:00.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:03.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:05.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that before I married you, I was dating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His real name is Jun'ya Tenma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, and I used to go with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:14.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was a nameless musician back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:20.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But on a certain day ten years ago, he suddenly disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:21.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I saw the papers for Gerard Tenma that we were going to sign a contract with,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.05,0:19:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was surprised to find that such a coincidence existed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time, Tenma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:35.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:43.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, I have a gift for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hand-made wine, something that you cannot get in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:53.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would like to taste the wine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There doesn't seem to be anything wrong with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.02,0:20:02.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's have juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, let's all have a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:12.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:19.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She's still on her guard, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:22.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, this sure is good wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:27.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:29.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes! I was baking a cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:34.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, will you go to the basement in the yard and get me the silver tea set?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:35.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:40.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will serve you all a special hand-made cake I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:41.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:49.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As one of the conditions of having your company publish "The Red Nocturne of Love",
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.78,0:20:53.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have slightly changed the lyrics and made a new arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:55.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A new arrangement?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:58.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gerard insisted on doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:02.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found this bunch of flowers at the entrance...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:03.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dahlias...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:07.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the language of flowers... Betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.77,0:21:08.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Betrayal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:15.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's secret, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:21.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tenma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, won't you play your music for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:23.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, you're here in person...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:26.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You attacked Misaki, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:33.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not {\i1}that{\i0} again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:35.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who else could've done it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:39.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to make preparations, so please leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you running away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:42.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you cut it out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:44.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They seem to be having an argument...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.54,0:21:46.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go check on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:51.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's Tenma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.30,0:21:59.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.10,0:22:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No! I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.83,0:22:04.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gerard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.83,0:22:10.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gerard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.38,0:22:12.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}T-This is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.03,0:23:49.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"The Red Nocturne of Love"!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.51,0:23:54.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Mr. Tenma wrote this song for Misaki{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} ten years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.24,0:23:58.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is this blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.36,0:24:00.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No, it's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.40,0:24:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the one who attacked Misaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.63,0:24:15.58,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.58,0:24:20.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Wine
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.56,0:24:25.56,Signs,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.56,0:24:21.79,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, the solution!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.79,0:24:22.82,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Cha-ri-ra-ri-ra-rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.82,0:24:23.76,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.76,0:24:24.91,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's the sound of a case being solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.91,0:24:25.56,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I see.
